---
title: Easy Seared Chicken Strips & Parmesan-Potato Salad with Celery Slaw
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of classic chicken shop flavours. Tender chicken strips get a lightly spiced
coating, with a warm, creamy potato salad and a crunchy celery slaw to round out the meal.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
